== Prospective Researchers/Students
We are looking for Postdoctoral Researchers, Ph.D. and master students who are interested in the following areas. Please feel free to contact me if you are interested. 
- Attitude Determination and Control, Formation Flying, Intention-Aware Autonomous Systems
- Fault Diagnosis and Tolerant Control, Learning-Aided Control Synthesis, Complex Mission Planning
- Constrained Control, Lyapunov-Based Controller Design, Control Allocation
